                <p>We envision a future where students from all backgrounds feel empowered to pursue their ideas boldly, regardless of experience level.</p>
                <p>By making technical creativity accessible and community-driven, we aim to foster lifelong innovators who carry their curiosity, leadership, and project experience beyond the classroom.</p>

                <h3 style="margin-top: 20px;">We believe in:</h3>
